
INSTALL
=======

Either
-----
```
pip install galpak
```

Or
--

download file from website and untar

tar xzvf galpak_1.x.y.gz

finished by perform a system installation
```
cd galpak/
sudo python setup.py install
```

Old Fashion
-----------
add the parent directory to PYTHONPATH


DEVELOPER INSTALL
-----------------

You'll need some extra python packages if you're a `galpak` developer :

```
pip install --user doit sphinx flask frozen-flask
```
